name: si568_project2_chatgpt
description: This is a web application built with React and FastAPI. It allows users to compare two PDF documents using OpenAI's ChatGPT. It is intended for use by urban planners and other professionals in assessing bid responses to a Request for Proposal (RFP). Users can freely use my code and deploy their own version, but will need an OpenAI API key to do so.
author: Alex Kutsupis
